Package: datr
Title: Organise projects for clean, repeatable, long-living productivity
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Josh", "Firth", , "drjoshfirth@gmailcom", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3815-8789"))
Description: Like Hadley Wickham's `usethis` package, this provides a set of `use_X` functions and other helpers that create useful and easy ways to ensure standardised, organised and repeatable proceses. MacOS or Windows agnostic.
